name: SJSH
description: The setting: You find your-self standing on what use to be a fine green lawn in front of an old building. You can tell it use to be a state hospital, but you know something is not right. Who knows, if you had been nicer in your 1st life, then you might not be in here in your 2nd. Too bad. Now there is only one way out......MY WAYYYYYYYyyyyyyy.......
